CommandScope
public static final class CommandScope.Builder extends com.google.protobuf.GeneratedMessage.Builder<CommandScope.Builder> implements CommandScopeOrBuilder
Defines the execution context for a command, determining which instances
and bots the command can affect. The scope also determines required permissions.
